works.description: This is a piece of outdoor furniture gadget freaks, party lovers and the green-minded would love to have in their backyard. The MIT SOFT Rockers are clean energy charging stations disguised as outdoor rocking lounge furniture. You can relax with your near and dear ones, and recharge your electronic devices at the same time. MIT Professor Sheila Kennedy and her team at Kennedy and Violich Architecture have created the SOFT Rockers. The SOFT Rocker, with its lighting loops at night, is sure to set the perfect ambiance for a playful, rejuvenating experience.
